POE::Component::Server::HTTPServer version 0.9.2
================================================

POE::Component::Server::HTTPServer is a POE-based HTTP server component.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

 - POE
 - MIME::Types
 - libwww-perl
 - (optional) The TemplateHandler request handler requires HTML::Template
   and HTML::Template::HashWrapper.

